high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the dining table.
Take the knife from the dining table.
Turn around move towards the sofa.
Cut the potato from the sofa.
Turn around move towards the pot.
Keep the knife on the pot.
Turn around move towards the sofa.
Take the potato from the sofa.
Turn around move towards the pot.
Keep the potato on the pot.
Take the pot on the table.
Turn around move towards the dining table.
Keep the pot on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Cut the potato, keep it on the pot, take the pot and keep it on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn left and go through this room to the table straight ahead and slightly to the left.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Go to the living room area on the other side of this room, approaching the sofa.
Slice the potato that is on the sofa.
Return to the table you got the knife from and turn to the fridge beside it.
Put the knife in the pot in the fridge.
Go back to the sliced potato on the sofa.
Pick up one potato slice.
Go back to the fridge.
Put the potato slice in the pot you put the knife in.
Remove that pot from the fridge.
Turn to the table you got the knife from.
Put the pot down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife and a potato slice in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn left to head down the passage and reach the dining table across the room.
Pick up the knife from the dining table.
Turn around to head to the living room on the right to reach the sofa.
Cut the potato with the knife on the sofa.
Turn left to reach the kitchen and head to the fridge on the right.
Put the knife in the pot in the fridge.
Turn around to reach the sofa in the living room.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sofa.
Turn left to head to the fridge in the kitchen.
Put the potato in the pot in the fridge.
Pick up the pot from the potato from the fridge.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Put the pot on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with the potato slice on the dining table.
